cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.NI, cs.LG, cs.SY

This paper deals with the security of the ADS-B system, which is a communication system used in air traffic management. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also proposes a two-stage deep neural network-based detector, which involves machine learning techniques, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) another likely category. The paper deals with the communication system and its security, which falls under the scope of cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The proposed detector involves deep neural networks, which is a machine learning technique, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another possible category. Finally, the paper deals with air traffic management, which involves control systems, making cs.SY (Systems and Control) a less likely but still possible category.
